  font-size: 15px;\n  letter-spacing: 2px;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n\n.kidnest-review-card p {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  line-height: 1.4;\n  margin: 0 0 10px;\n  color: #0B61CD;\n}\n\n.kidnest-review-card span {\n  font-size: 13px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #0B61CD;\n}\n\n@keyframes kidnest-scroll {\n  from { transform: translateX(0); }\n  to { transform: translateX(-50%); }\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 749px) {\n  .kidnest-reviews-marquee {\n    min-height: 150px;\n  }\n\n  .kidnest-review-card {\n    width: 240px;\n    min-height: 170px;\n  }\n}\n</style>",
